<TITLE> England defender Richards arrested for alleged assault </TITLE>
<TEXT>
 LONDON, Feb 5 (bdnews24.com/Reuters) - Manchester City defender Micah Richards has been arrested on suspicion of assault after an incident outside a nightclub in northwest England, police said on Thursday. Richards, 20, was detained after going to a police station by appointment on Wednesday. He was questioned over an allegation of assault outside a nightclub in Hale, in the south of the city, on Christmas Eve. A club spokesman told the Manchester Evening News that Richards "vigorously denies any involvement"
